---
title: Pan-Seared Steaks and Mushroom Gravy with Bacon Roasted Brussels Sprouts
description: Steak night will never be the same after you try this! Prepare your tastebuds for juicy steak and smashed potatoes covered in flavour-packed mushroom gravy, and yes, you read that right, Brussels sprouts roasted with BACON. You can thank us later!
